{"tid":2349500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"42宗新確診，42日以來最少","createTime":"2021-01-01T15:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T15:13:31.000Z","uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ff2006cdf453b655206acfdf107280ab572913","tid":2349500,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/43370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F43370&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=7541ddff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F43370&h=d13e008a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/43370</a><br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】本港新增42宗新型肺炎確診，是42日以來最少。衞生防護中心及醫管局感激市民和醫護過去一年辛苦抗疫，確診數字雖然稍為回落，但擔心長假期後有機會反彈。<br />\n<br />\n新年首日錄得42宗確診，是11月20日以來最少，疫情是否開始有曙光？衞生防護中心表示長假期仍然很多聚會，希望疫情不會因而反彈，衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君：「過去一年大家一起抗疫，都知道大家很辛苦，因為很多事情平常可以做，現在都很困難，無論逛街、吃飯。希望大家再忍耐，因為未來可能有疫苗。希望來了，疫苗來了，希望生活可以恢復正常。」"},{"pid":"89578803578c58ecd61f287af87fb62a46e8dd6e","tid":2349500,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:12:22.000Z","msg":"42 = 42 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2aacac76dc828509093f472bb272fe73aebe9c","tid":2349500,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:13:31.000Z","msg":"但係仲有3-8座大廈俾衞生署屈緊檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[求推] 衞生署 強制檢測名單 又双叒叕有錯？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2349363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2349363</a>"}]}